Tableize
=============

This plugin is used to handle table ordering, indexing or searching.


Example
=======

app/models/sortable.rb

class Sortable < ActiveRecord::Base

sortable_with :i, 'id'
sortable_with :n, 'Name'
sortable_with :z, 'zip'
sortable_with :a, 'age'
default_order :XXX

end




